snippet.description:

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Tiku Weds Sheru - Official Trailer | Nawazuddin Siddiqui, Avneet Kaur | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video Presents
Tiku Weds Sheru Official Trailer
Directed by Sai Kabir
Starring Nawazuddin Siddiqui and Avneet Kaur
Produced by Kangana Ranaut

Official Release Date June 23, 2023 on Prime Video 

About:
Sheru and Tiku are marginalized souls from the underprivileged strata of society. They are ambitious for a better life but, life has different plans for them. Shiraz, popularly known as Sheru, hails from Bhopal, a small-town in India. Sheru comes to Mumbai in search of a better life. Being semi-literate, he works as a pimp for a local don, Shahid Bhai, and also as a junior artist as a decoy job, where he finds girls for his pimping business. He risks everything to win the confidence of his boss to be promoted as an equal partner. Taslim, aka Tiku, lives with her large conservative Muslim family in Bhopal. To break free from her family, she runs away to Delhi under the pretext of higher studies, where she falls in love with a man from a different religion, but her family marry her off to the first available eligible bachelor, Sheru. Sheru accepts the proposal in desperation of repaying a loan, while Tiku sees Sheru as her passport to freedom. However, Sheru falls in love with Tiku but they get caught between the chaos of the underworld, drugs, and romance and face one tragedy after the other without any time to deal with their sorrow.

Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video‚Äôs exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ‚Çπ599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website.

In this exceptional episode of The Ranveer Show Podcast, we are pleased to welcome one of the most prestigious personalities of the Government of India, Dr. Subrahmanyam Jaishankar. He is an Indian diplomat and politician, serving as the Minister of External Affairs of the Government of India.

In this informative episode, Dr. Subrahmanyam Jaishankar talked about topics that are closely related to Geopolitics. He shares his experience of working with Prime Minister Narendra Modi and what are the challenges he has to face as the Minister of External Affairs. He further discusses the Role of Artificial Intelligence and Quantum Computing in the field of Geopolitics and put light on the situation of Brain Drain in the Country. 

This is one of the most special episodes that I‚Äôve been a part of considering my interest in Geopolitics and India‚Äôs bright future. Being in conversation with Dr. Subrahmanyam Jaishankar was an overwhelming yet fantastic experience.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3799 | 16 June 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3799: Sapna Ki Love Story
--------------------------------------------------------
Everyone has arrived together to perform the shagun ritual of Pyaarelal and Sapna, but Pyaarelal seems to be missing. Someone said that he had visited the nearby temple before the ritual. Pyaarelal returns shortly, but he is accompanied by another young man named Swapnil. Sapna gets flabbergasted when she sees this new fellow. Pyaarelal talks about how he met Swapnil. Swapnil turns out to be Sapna's ex-boyfriend, who left her for a lucrative job offer in Canada. Swapnil's job didn't work out, and now he has returned, but Sapna has moved on. According to Pyaarelal, Swapnil and Sapna still have feelings for each other, so he decides to unite them. Will Pyaarelal sacrifice for Sapna's love story this time?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3799, 16 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

--------------------------------------------------------
Finally, Pyaarelal's shagun ritual begins. Everyone dresses in yellow attire because Pyaarelal has chosen Sapna as his bride. Here is #Adipurush Movie Review, Rating and public talk. #Adipurush is a Devoinal entertainer. #Adipurush's story deals with Lord Rama. #Adipurush Review reveals positives and negatives of the film in detail. 

 #Prabhas #KritiSanon are the lead actor in #Adipurush movie. Sunny singh and others are the key cast in #Adipurush. Om Raut directed the film #Adipurush. Ajay Atul did music for #Adipurush movie. T series produced the film and Peoples Media released the film in Telugu. Catch complete review of #Adipurush Movie in Telugu in the video.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 53 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 14th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

It is necessary for every road user to be aware of traffic signs and driving rules and regulations. Traffic signs can give you important information that can ensure your safety and the safety of those around you and awareness of road rules can lower chances of accidents.

Episode 3797: Kalpana Ka Final Decision
--------------------------------------------------------
Kalpana and her parents get upset when they discover that Popatlal has changed his name to Pyaarelal on purpose. Kalpana questions him about the reason behind his name change, to which Pyaarelal answers that, as per Vinu Kaka's sayings, he took this decision. Kalpana isn't convinced by Pyaarelal's reason, and she decides to call off the wedding. Kalpana tells Pyaarelal that he should have at least informed her about the new name. She also tells Pyaarelal that his fickle-minded nature makes it difficult for her to trust him. Pyaarelal, aka Popatlal, gets melancholy that he has to stay a bachelor forever. Watch the episode to learn what happens next!

snippet.title: Washington DC to New York - An American Truck Yatra!
snippet.description:
Continuing on my journey to listen to a variety of voices, I recently went on a 190 km 'American Truck Yatra' from Washington DC to New York. 

Much like my Truck Yatra from Delhi to Chandigarh here in India, I enjoyed a candid heart-to-heart conversation- this time centred around the everyday lives of Indian-origin Truck drivers in America.

Was happy to find out that our brothers in America earn fair wages, and work in a system that is focused on the 'Driver's comfort'. 

The hardworking Truck drivers' community in India deserves a life of dignity too, and an inclusive vision that takes them forward is bound have a positive cascading effect on the economy of our entire country.

#rahulgandhi, #‡§∞‡§æ‡§π‡•Å‡§≤_‡§ó‡§æ‡§Ç‡§ß‡•Ä, #bharatjodoyatra, #RahulKiAmericaTruckYatra

https://youtu.be/LZ9fOkHL6VY

localized.title: Washington DC to New York - An American Truck Yatra!
localized.description:
Continuing on my journey to listen to a variety of voices, I recently went on a 190 km 'American Truck Yatra' from Washington DC to New York. 

Much like my Truck Yatra from Delhi to Chandigarh here in India, I enjoyed a candid heart-to-heart conversation- this time centred around the everyday lives of Indian-origin Truck drivers in America.

Was happy to find out that our brothers in America earn fair wages, and work in a system that is focused on the 'Driver's comfort'. 

The hardworking Truck drivers' community in India deserves a life of dignity too, and an inclusive vision that takes them forward is bound have a positive cascading effect on the economy of our entire country.

snippet.title: Vannarapettayila - Lyrical Video | Maaveeran | Sivakarthikeyan, Aditi Shankar | Bharath Sankar
snippet.description:
Here is the second single 'Vannarapettayila' from 'Maaveeran' starring Sivakarthikeyan, Aditi Shankar & Others. Directed by Mandela Fame Madonne Ashwin and Produced by Shanthi Talkies. 

Song Credits: 
Vannarapettayila
Composed, Arranged and Produced by Bharath Sankar

At Hafod Mastering, UK

Manikandan Uthirapathi

Lyrics:
Vannaarapettayula oru
vavvaalu aengiduchaam
Pollaadha Kaadhal vara
adhu lovebird-ah maariduchaam

Karunkallelaam
kannaadi voodaachaam
veral pattaalae
ice cream-um soodaachaam

cell-elaam violent mode aachaam
Jagame jolly aachaam

Kokki potu izhukaama
Sarinjaanae Lesa
Konjam ava Sirichaale
Karanjaan Sarvesa

Paakaama avalum ponaale
Power-um Cut aachaam
Oru Nodi dhaan paathaa
Kodi minsaaram usurula undaachaam

Yaarodum edhuvum pesaama
Thalayae rendaachaam
Andha kadhaya ketaa Oosi Pattaasum
Adhiradi Gundaachaam

Kaathaadi kooda
Kai meeri pochaam
Aeroplane aaga yengi yengi
Mela parakudhu

Kannaala paatezhudhi
Ava Themmaangu paadavachaa
Illaadha kaadhal vara
Kola Kuthaattam poda vachaa

Vannaarapettayula oru
vavvaalu aengiduchaam
Pollaadha Kaadhal vara
adhu lovebird-ah maariduchaam

Yaar sonnaalum kekkala
Summave maapula
thannaala daaladichaan

Ipo sandhosham thaangala
Aanaalum thoongala
Innaanu kelu machaan

snippet.description:

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Harleen and Nehmat offer to prepare a feast to celebrate Ekam's return to the house. Nehmat requests Sartaj to cooperate with her when he refuses to let her go through such trouble. Will Sartaj agree to Nehmat's request?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! snippet.title: Indians In Summer Vacation | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys ,
This Video all the things that happen in summer vacations . Every Indian in summer vacations going on vacation with family to hill stations like shimla , manali , mussoorie , darjeeling , haridwar , rishikesh . Indian moms dealing with holiday homework given by school teachers during summer break , Family trips , horse ridding , trekking , hiking . watching sunsets , sunrise at famous hill tops , creating memories clicking pictures , tourist locations and rush of people and traffic jams , mother excited to go vacation getting her beauty regime by parlour didi , waxing , facial , threading , bleach , dtan , shopping from sarojini nagar to travel , buying gifts for relatives on vacay , travelling by train enjoying , singing eating train food , road trip with family , stopping at dhaba , mom feeding her home cooked food puri aloo jeera sabzi , middle class dad driving on highway , kids singing fighting taking pictures on the way to himachal and so much more ..
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family especially guests .. Comment down your Fav Part, 
Like, Share and 
Subscribe to our Channel - http://bit.ly/thepaayaljain | Press Bell Icon
